Windows Registry Editor Version 5.00

## Setup Pixel Graphics Video Player File Association ##
; OS: Windows 7
; Change: After Restart
; Created by: Robert Jordan
; Published:  2 Feb 2018

; Notes: This will add "Open With" file associations for Pixel Graphics Video Player.
;        The paths for the icons and executables will need to be changed.
;        Paths that need to be changed are marked with "### CHANGE THIS PATH ###".
;        The new paths should be constant.

;;======== FILE EXTENSIONS ===================;;

# AVI
; Classes Root
[HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT\.avi\OpenWithProgIds]
"PGVideoPlayer"=""
; Local Machine
[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Classes\.avi\OpenWithProgIds]
"PGVideoPlayer"=""

;;--------------------------------;;

